Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:15.33,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:36.01,Show_Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(1075,0)\blur2\move(320,300,320,290)\org(320,180)\fs58\t(\fs50)}The Faraway Paladin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:39.87,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Unde crezi că te duci?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:42.71,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Unde?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:45.43,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Să omor bestiile demonice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:49.70,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,De unul singur?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:51.32,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:53.80,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mă îndoiesc că ai putea ține pasul cu mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:57.99,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,De asta trebuie să-l protejez.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:02.88,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Nu-ți face griji. Va fi bine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:05.91,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mă voi ocupa eu de tot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:10.13,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Voi omorî himera și întreaga gloată de bestii demonice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:14.15,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Dacă sunt demoni care le controlează, atunci, îi voi ucide și pe ei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:18.30,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Șe pare că ăsta e genul de monstru care sunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:21.54,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.32,0:01:25.74,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Gata cu prostiile!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:27.53,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Revino-ți odată!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:28.99,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Idiotule!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:34.72,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Oh, deci așa vor decurge lucrurile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:38.09,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Asta e tot ce poți, Meneldor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:48.31,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,La naiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:55.83,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Nu-l pot lăsa să mă urmărească.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:00.52,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,La naiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:04.69,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,La naiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:07.51,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,La naiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:09.00,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,La naiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:13.70,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Presupun că i-aș putea rupe o mână.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:28.75,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Găsește pe cineva să te vindece.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:32.03,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Nu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.07,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Nu am terminat încă!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:38.21,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Oh? Te opui mai mult decât credeam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.56,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Ce ar trebui să fac?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:43.45,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Oare să folosesc Cuvinte ca să-l țin pe loc?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.11,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Nu, îl voi strânge de gât și-l voi face să-și piardă cunoștin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:48.42,Main - Top,Menel,0,0,0,,Gnomilor, oh, gnomilor, încleștați-vă pumnii!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.68,Main - Top,Menel,0,0,0,,Și folosiți-i ca să vă doborâți inamicul!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.62,Main,Will,0,0,0,,O incantație inutilă.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:57.36,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Nu! Dacă mă voi feri, vraja îl va lovi pe Menel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:08.15,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,What's this crap about \Nfixing everything alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.79,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Ești doar un fricos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.26,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Chiar trebuia să mergi atât de departe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.01,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.48,Main,Will,0,0,0,,We were only together because \Nthings worked out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.46,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Nu ai niciun motiv să faci asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:28.94,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Da, așa este.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.82,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I have no reason to go out of my way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:35.11,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,to stop an emotionally unstable \Ncoward who's completely lost it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.12,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,just because he got his \Nass handed to him once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:38.65,Main,Will,0,0,0,,În acest caz...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:39.41,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Dar...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.40,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Ești prietenul meu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:44.85,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Iar prietenii rămân împreună.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.74,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Dacă prietenul meu o ia razna, trebuie să-l readuc cu picioarele pe pământ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:51.08,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Menel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.31,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,You don't know much about your own origins,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:56.44,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,and you're clueless about the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:58.84,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,There've been times when I \Nthought you seemed suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.53,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,But you're a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.31,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I know you're trying to do things right, \Nand doing your best at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:11.57,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,You saved my life, you saved that village...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:15.37,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,We traveled together, we fought together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.89,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,And I enjoyed spending time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:22.26,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to you from the bottom of my \Nheart for sending off those villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:27.87,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Will, you are my friend, \Nand I don't abandon my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.48,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Well, you still wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.82,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:44.86,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I'm still weaker than you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.30,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,but just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.62,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I'll catch up before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.51,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Menel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.99,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I'll prove to you soon enough
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.53,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,that you're no monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:02.38,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:06.05,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'll wait. I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:09.65,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Man, you're a real pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:14.53,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Sorry. I kinda lost control of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.54,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Well, it happens—ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.63,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'll heal that—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.29,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,But a surrender's a surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:22.63,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,That means I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:26.61,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I only surrendered because \Nyou wouldn't give it a rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:27.58,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Keep whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:30.59,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:36.94,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,And so we kept exchanging \Ndumb jokes and laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:36.25,Main - Top,Menel,0,0,0,,What a pretty sight. The moon's \Ncongratulating me on my victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:39.19,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,What? Want me to break your other arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.63,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,It was my first ever argument with a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.96,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and I guess I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.85,Main,Adventurer,0,0,0,,Oh, you're back, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:48.35,Main,Adventurer,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.49,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Will! Menel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:53.07,Main,Adventurer,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:54.79,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,You jerks! You had me worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:57.08,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Sorry, Bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:58.51,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,Will...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:02.70,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, would you \Nplease tell me what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.00,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.01,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,That's an illness of the strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:19.68,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,The stronger you are, \Nthe harder it hits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:22.90,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Depending on the case, it can even kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:26.47,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry for \Nmaking all of you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:29.96,Main,Will,0,0,0,,But I'm all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.99,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,You were just stuck in bed not long ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:40.62,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,and you were off slugging it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.66,Main,AdventurerC,0,0,0,,We even set a trap for a surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.49,Main,AdventurerC,0,0,0,,That chimera's got no chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:46.66,Main,Adventurer,0,0,0,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:49.65,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I've got a debt to repay to that bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.62,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I won't be humiliated like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:55.21,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,You're gonna fight that thing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:57.86,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're going for a return match.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:07:00.03,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I refuse to just get beat \Nup and leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:03.15,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I'll split all three of that \Ndemon beast's heads open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:09.41,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Chimeras don't occur naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:12.78,Main,Will,0,0,0,,That thing is, without a doubt, \Nthe product of a demonic ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.54,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Let's take all of them out at once, \Nbefore they can escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:18.97,Main,AdventurerD,0,0,0,,So soon after it roughed us up that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.76,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,I can't just give up and leave it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:22.03,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,Let's bust 'em up good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:24.81,Main,AdventurerD,0,0,0,,All right, guess we should \Nround up some help, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:28.03,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,It's gonna be a good, fun, \Nstupid-as-hell adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:30.21,Main,Will,0,0,0,,You'll get one silver coin \Nfor a demon beast's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:33.17,Main,Will,0,0,0,,and ten gold coins for the demon boss's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.96,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,After that, we spent a few days \Ngetting a force together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:54.79,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,sent out several rounds of scouts, \Nand made our preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:57.18,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,We didn't arrange any special tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:01.56,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,We'd just get enough people together, \Nmake preparations ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.61,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and face our enemy head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.31,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Let's set up our formation and gear here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:19.82,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Anna and the other priests, \Nplease support us from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:20.94,Main,Anna,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:24.47,Main,Will,0,0,0,,When we're all ready, we'll send \Nour front line to the battle zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.54,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,If we can wipe out all of those,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:36.98,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,this whole area's gonna be \Na whole lot more peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:38.58,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.91,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Let's wipe them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:43.32,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Sometimes you say the wildest \Nthings so casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:44.30,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:53.81,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I'll back you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:56.24,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Okay. I'm counting on you, Menel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.73,Main,Will,0,0,0,,We'll break through head-on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:05.43,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,By Volt's blade of lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:08.14,Main,AdventurerF,0,0,0,,Burn bright, Blaze's flames of courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:12.40,Main,AdventurerG,0,0,0,,Whirl, send us a tailwind of good fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.35,Main,AdventurerB,0,0,0,,Grant us the divine protection \Nof all the virtuous gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.55,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.51,Main - Top,Sorcerer,0,0,0,,Sagitta Flammeum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.29,Words,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Flame Arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.17,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,It's war!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.24,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Stand ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:39.80,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Goddess of flux, repel the \Npoisons that rain down upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:40.88,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,Fortis...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:40.85,Words,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Strong
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:41.80,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,Vita!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:41.60,Words,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Life
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.65,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,How could I say I'd fix all this alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:12.84,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I was never any more than \None factor in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.85,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,The battlefield isn't so easy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:17.46,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,that just one dose of penetrating \Nstrength is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:22.47,Main,Will,0,0,0,,By the flame of Gracefeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.73,Main,Ethelbald,0,0,0,,According to reports,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:32.64,Main,Ethelbald,0,0,0,,the campaign to eliminate the demon \Nbeasts should be starting by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:36.77,Main,Ethelbald,0,0,0,,I wonder, will these great Wyvern Killers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:40.61,Main,Ethelbald,0,0,0,,succeed in a new heroic feat \Nfor the bards to sing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:41.74,Main,Bagley,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:46.56,Main,Bagley,0,0,0,,The temple has bent over backwards \Nto facilitate that novice boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:49.24,Main,Bagley,0,0,0,,If he fails to succeed in this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:51.53,Main,Bagley,0,0,0,,he will not be worthy of our backing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:53.58,Main,Ethelbald,0,0,0,,By the way, Bishop,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.77,Main,Ethelbald,0,0,0,,I hear you entrusted your daughter, Anna,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:59.95,Main,Ethelbald,0,0,0,,and many other brilliant \Npriests to the paladin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:04.08,Main,Bagley,0,0,0,,Losing valuable talent to the philanthropic \Nexploits of such a novice
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:06.27,Main,Bagley,0,0,0,,has caused nothing but trouble for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.40,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.93,Main,Will,0,0,0,,The abandoned remains of a monastery?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:18.00,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Looks like we're the first ones here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.64,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Be careful. There might be traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.01,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,Omnia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:34.84,Words,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Everything
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:35.99,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,Vanitas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:35.84,Words,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1}In Vain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.28,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,Erasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.09,Words,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Erasure
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:44.90,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:47.19,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,It was waiting in ambush with Invisibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:50.74,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Careful, Will. \NThis thing's pretty damn smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:54.20,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Do you think maybe it's \Ngot some demon in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.66,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Are you after the High King?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:01.14,Main,Chimera,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:03.61,Main,Chimera,0,0,0,,You know the High King's seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:07.00,Main,Chimera,0,0,0,,Are you a warrior sent by one of the gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:09.89,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,That answer... I'm certain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:15.05,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Basically, this is like taking \Na square on a chess board.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:17.86,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,The city of the dead, where \Nthe High King was sealed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:20.65,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,isn't yet under either side's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:25.26,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,If the demons take control, \Nthey'll undo the seal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:27.55,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and disaster will ravage \Nthe continent again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.81,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,But if the people take control,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.74,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,the seal will likely become even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.65,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,The demons are in a position
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:37.62,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,where they need to keep Beast Woods \Npermanently devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:41.19,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,They need to keep it in a state of \Nchaos, destitution, and lawlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:45.95,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,That's why they're commanding demon beasts \Nto attack villages and keep the pressure on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:49.21,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,They can't let mankind \Nadvance any further south.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:52.30,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,They can't let people head toward the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:55.62,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,They can't let them think \Nthere's hope in the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:59.40,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,If you consider the existence of their king,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:02.96,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,it's incredibly easy to figure \Nout what their objective is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.94,Main,Will,0,0,0,,In the name of the goddess of flux, \NI will destroy all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:12.37,Main,Chimera,0,0,0,,Oh? But wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:16.66,Main,Chimera,0,0,0,,There seems to be some sort of mistake, \Nor perhaps a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.09,Main,Will,0,0,0,,A misunderstanding, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.45,Main,Chimera,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:23.10,Main,Chimera,0,0,0,,In truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:35.74,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Demons like to stick to the classics \Nin their surprise attacks, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:39.01,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Menel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:39.85,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:42.08,Main - Top,Chimera,0,0,0,,Sagitta Flammeum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.96,Words,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Flame Arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:43.74,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I'm not takin' that hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.88,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Sylphs, sylphs, maidens of wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.64,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Gracefeel, grant us your protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.26,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Don't stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:55.13,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Divert it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.16,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Gnomes, O gnomes, slip underfoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:02.32,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Tighten, bind, and tie it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:15.18,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,It has multiple heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.46,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,If each one takes a different \Nreflexive action,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.38,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,they're sure to end up confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:22.54,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,This demon beast is unnatural \Nin terms of living beings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:28.09,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I don't need to score a clean \Nvictory in one strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:31.07,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I just need to fight it the right \Nway and win by being better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:33.84,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I don't need a flashy secret technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:35.81,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I'll just use all three of their teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.51,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and do what it takes to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.73,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,That's the fighting style \Nthat's best for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:45.91,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Maidens of wind, \Nbless this arrow with your kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:57.25,Main,Will,0,0,0,,That's one down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:07.00,Main,ChimeraMale,0,0,0,,Although I detest this dragon power, \Nyou leave me with no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.15,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:12.92,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,This one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:13.73,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Menel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.07,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Get back a little farther.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:17.66,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'll strike it down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:20.09,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I was raised on Mary's bread,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:22.30,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and my arms bear Mater's stigma,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:25.49,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,so poisons don't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:28.99,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'd like some \Nglory of your own, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:42.91,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Gnomes, O gnomes, clench your fists!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:45.16,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Use them to strike the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.81,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,There's nowhere to run to the left or right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:54.63,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:56.65,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,Acceleratio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.43,Words,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Accelerate
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.68,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Gnomes, O gnomes, slip underfoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:05.64,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Tighten, bind, and tie it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:21.54,Main,Will,0,0,0,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.40,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.22,Main,Will,0,0,0,,On to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:30.94,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:43.05,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:46.25,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Reystov?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:49.06,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,I'll be taking those ten gold coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:51.32,Main,Will,0,0,0,,What?! He beat us to it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:53.32,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,You're kidding! How'd you do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:54.79,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Came around from the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:58.32,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,Since you guys were taking \Ncare of the chimera for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.05,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,it was actually pretty easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:03.53,Main,Will,0,0,0,,That's Reystov the Penetrator for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:05.49,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,He's way too good at getting \Nthe jump on people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:09.35,Main,Reystov,0,0,0,,You have to be, if you want to \Nget to the strongest opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:12.19,Main,AdventurerC,0,0,0,,Careful! No telling what \Nkinda traps are in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:14.55,Main,AdventurerD,0,0,0,,Heh, we're the first ones here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.60,Main,AdventurerE,0,0,0,,And those ten gold coins are ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:17.11,Main,AdventurerE,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.45,Main,AdventurerA,0,0,0,,To our victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:47.23,Episode_Title,Title,0,0,0,,Episodul 12 \NPaladinul Ținutul Îndepărtat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:51.60,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Ce părere ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:54.75,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'm happy, but still kinda embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.63,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I feel like you embellished a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:59.87,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,This kinda thing is supposed \Nto be a little embellished!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:02.17,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Hey, someone who gets it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:05.24,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,I'll write a song about you next, Menel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:05.94,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:09.78,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll give you the nickname \N"Meneldor the Beautiful"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.97,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,The one who walks the hero's path \Nalong with the Faraway Paladin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:16.44,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that gonna make people \Nthink I'm actually a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.44,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,And you can be Will's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:19.45,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Don't you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.39,Main - Top,Bee,0,0,0,,Aw, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.50,Main - Top,Menel,0,0,0,,It is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:23.92,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,After his vehement objections, \NMenel's nickname was revised
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:27.51,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,from "Meneldor the Beautiful" \Nto "Meneldor of Swift Wings."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.88,Main,Will,0,0,0,,It's so much more lively now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.95,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,And it's gonna get more and \Nmore lively from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:37.32,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:39.59,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,What're you talking about? \NOf course it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:42.02,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,The threat of the demons and \Ndemon beasts has faded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:45.52,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,People searching for new lands \Nare gonna flock to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:48.49,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,There'll probably be problems, \Ntoo, but that's how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.33,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:54.00,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Also, I'll say this since you'll \Nfind out eventually anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:56.79,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,The villagers are building a shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.39,Main,Will,0,0,0,,A shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.23,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,The one they talked about \Nback at the meeting hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.92,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,They made an altar to hold votive candles,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:05.42,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,and they decided to make \Nit a shrine to Gracefeel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:07.83,Main,Will,0,0,0,,To the goddess of light?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:12.38,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,It's the first step toward \Ngrowing her following again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:15.53,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,By the way, what are you gonna do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:16.49,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Next?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.14,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Well, there's still a lot of clean-up to—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:20.39,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,I mean after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:21.35,Main,Will,0,0,0,,After that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:23.44,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Gonna be the lord of a domain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.68,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Huh? A lord? For what domain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:27.87,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,The villages of Beast Woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:28.67,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:29.59,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:33.26,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:37.09,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I am a knight, but a \Nsingle-generation one with no land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:39.38,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'm no different from an \Nadventurer, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.51,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Is that seriously what you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.28,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.82,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,For real? You didn't even \Nknow what you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:46.97,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.94,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Just so I'm clear here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:51.97,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,If you wanted to do business in this \Nforest, who would you talk to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:53.24,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Tonio?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:55.78,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,But didn't most of the funds come from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.23,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.10,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:21:02.09,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,First of all, you're a paladin with the \Ngoddess of light's divine protection
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.93,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,and the approval of both the \Ncountry and the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:06.31,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,You have all kinds of power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:09.57,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,On top of that, you have the military \Nauthority to gather all these adventurers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:13.37,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,and by arbitrating for the villages, \Nyou effectively have jurisdiction over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.46,Main,Will,0,0,0,,So, um, you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.25,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,In the process of exterminating the demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:19.57,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,you took control of the flow \Nof goods, ruling power,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:24.05,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,military force, jurisdiction, \Nand every other kind of authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:27.51,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,If you say you don't wanna do all that now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.12,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,{\i1}that{\i0} would be the disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:32.56,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Are you saying... \Nyou seriously didn't realize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:35.81,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.96,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I just hoped I could do \Nsomething about the demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:43.53,Main,Will,0,0,0,,and improve the impoverished conditions \Nin the villages a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:50.32,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,From there, I just thought I'd make a \Nslick exit, like Blood and the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:52.78,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Um... Menel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:57.13,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Wh-What do I do? Should I start \Nby getting people together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:21:59.88,Main,Will,0,0,0,,You've already got a merchant \Nand priests who know the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:01.21,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,If you need more,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:03.96,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,just have the crown prince \Nset you up with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:09.34,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Cum naiba am ajuns în această situație?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:10.61,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Spune-mi, te rog,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:12.79,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,zeița mea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:17.02,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.68,0:22:22.35,Main,Will,0,0,0,,That does sound like it might \Nbe a goal worth working toward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:24.87,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,It's probably gonna be some \Ndamn hard work, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.21,0:22:29.05,Main,Will,0,0,0,,But as long as I have all of you, \NI'm sure it'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:33.84,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mă vei ajuta, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:37.59,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Of, fie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:40.06,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Te voi ajuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:43.26,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mai întâi, trebuie să aflăm ce plănuiesc demonii...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:44.18,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Cui îi pasă?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:46.80,Main,Menel,0,0,0,,Just grab the bastards and crush 'em \Nas soon as you find 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:48.16,Main,Will,0,0,0,,That's so violent...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:51.66,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Hei! Will! Menel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.88,0:22:56.22,Main,Bee,0,0,0,,Nu vă mai ascundeți în micuța voastră lume și veniți aici!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:02.03,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,If more people come in and \Neverything goes well,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:07.32,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,maybe we'll be able to return to that city.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:10.92,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Maybe we can make the city of the dead
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.38,0:23:15.84,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,a regular city where living \Npeople can laugh together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:23.19,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Up on the hill where \NMary and Blood's graves are,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:25.38,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,the laughter of children will resound,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:28.15,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,and the sounds of people working \Nto make a living will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:36.65,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Somehow, that seemed like \Nsuch a wonderful thing to me.
